<item>
            <title>[AVRO-1784] Should have a C++ json encoder that pretty prints.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1784</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would nice to allow json ouput to be pretty printed. It&apos;s obviously possible to post-process, but that frequently re-orders which results in the problem described in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1636&quot; title=&quot;C++ JsonDecoder expects json object to be ordered&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;AVRO-1636&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;AVRO-1636&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. In addition it obviously requires another pass through the data.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll attach a patch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
