                            <comment id="15177070" author="comm@squotd.net" created="Thu, 3 Mar 2016 03:08:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Thiru. It&apos;s obviously not urgent; just trying to get it on the radar.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15177080" author="comm@squotd.net" created="Thu, 3 Mar 2016 03:13:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;BTW, I tried to make the change minimal but the templates defeated me to some degree. Perhaps there&apos;s a better way to do this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
